John Edwards Indicted After Probe Finds Campaign Funds Used to Hide Affair

-- B y   J u s t i n   B l u m
-- 
2011-06-03T14:27:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-03/john-edwards-indicted-after-probe-finds-campaign-funds-used-to-hide-affair.html
Former U.S. presidential candidate
 John Edwards  was charged with conspiracy and illegal campaign
contributions, a Justice Department spokeswoman said today.  Edwards, a Democrat, has been the subject of a two-year
grand jury investigation into whether he used campaign funds to
conceal his relationship with filmmaker Rielle Hunter while
running for president in 2008.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Justin Blum in Washington at 
 jblum4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David E. Rovella at 
 drovella@bloomberg.net  